txt.en: Defeat Corsair captains in Hata Kebir ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Nimithil can be found in Ost Anglebed in north-central Lebennin.\n\nYou have slain many of the forces in Hata Kebir and set flame to their banners. You should now return to Nimithil.
Defeated Corsair captains in Hata Kebir ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Talk to Nimithil in Ost Anglebed

'The people of Lebennin will rest well this night, but I am certain I shall have need of your aid again soon. Their numbers are great, and a single assault shall not be enough.\n\n'You have done well, [placeholder].'

'I know well that you have made great inroads against the Haradrim and Corsairs on our shores, but we cannot allow them time to recover.

'With Azgarz√¥r defeated, we now have a chance to push them from our lands, and I will not see it slip away from us.

'Go once again to their great camp, defeat many of their numbers, and lay waste to their standards. As their force dwindles and their spirit diminishes, it is my hope they shall flee back to Umbar.'
Although they are cut off from their brethren in Pelargir, the Haradrim and Corsair forces in Hata Kebir still pose a substantial threat to the people of Lebennin.
Hata Kebir can be found far to the south-east of Ost Anglebed in Lebennin.\n\nNimithil has asked you to assault the Haradrim and Corsair forces in Hata Kebir.
